{"tid":209102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"A_Milik 意大利統一事件整合","createTime":"2017-04-20T03:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T14:50:36.000Z","uid":4221,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"464fdcced10491813c09f9195bd39f04471b8589","tid":209102,"uid":4221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote><br />\n事源系學術台出文反應熱烈<br />\n之後中途潛水 突然上水承諾會再出文之後走數<br />\n因樓主深受波台手足支持 冇文再幫佢推po令到事件廣為人知 引發今日聲討行動<br />\n<br />\n有冇人對意大利統一有興趣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/72553?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/72553?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先係自稱唔舒服走數 但係自推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/110943_cbd5c2e85cd9af68dd2e573a868b49b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F110943_cbd5c2e85cd9af68dd2e573a868b49b6.jpg&h=1c2bfadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眾波台手足仍然推po 相隔一個月直至19/2<br />\n<br />\nA_Milik 先上水回應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/111038_b9050b7ac2cd1ff7fa8e0fb61c925a52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F111038_b9050b7ac2cd1ff7fa8e0fb61c925a52.jpg&h=a46e4c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後回應係21/2     就沒有以後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位手足只要提及 <span style=\"color: red;\">意大利 統一 找數</span>等關鍵字<br />\n<br />\nA_Milik便會自動深潛 不作理會<br />\n<br />\n同場加載柒事一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1a7h7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1a7h7v.jpg&h=1c4d3bc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f202894ad097968ae8311a121ed99066bee92eb","tid":209102,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b73465636010f39da89328c98126feb736d2e2","tid":209102,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗開咁多個牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e9018db491f24f1e15a6dccd334227e6d68749","tid":209102,"uid":37604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e195f5e625818cc9fec83f3df74a805b227a0349","tid":209102,"uid":37604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗開咁多個牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7702f1c377b621191dea8057d6620335837b4241","tid":209102,"uid":3832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"係啲post留完言比人提佢意大利統一個陣就潛撚哂水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83310748eabae03726829cba8b73ad6937f67616","tid":209102,"uid":4221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"最近多唔多手足想去意大利玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/209030/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/209030/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n波台聯署要求A_Milk盡快出文<br />\n<a href=\"https://